md:
giải nghĩa từ "shines" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

* Shines ( Verb )
	+ Meaning: To give out a bright light; to be very bright and attractive.
	+ Example: The diamond shines brightly on her finger.
	+ Related words: sparkle, glitter, radiate, beam
	+ Antonyms: dims, fades, dulls

* Shines ( Verb )
	+ Meaning: To do something very well; to be very good at something.
	+ Example: She shines in her role as a leader.
	+ Related words: excels, stands out, surpasses, outshines
	+ Antonyms: fails, struggles, falls short

* Shines ( Noun )
	+ Meaning: A bright, shiny surface or appearance.
	+ Example: The car's new paint job has a beautiful shine.
	+ Related words: gloss, luster, polish, sheen
	+ Antonyms: dullness, matte, roughness
